transformers_text:
285 22 "Obtain the 5 Keys! The Straw Hat Pirates vs. CP9!"Transliteration: "Itsutsu no Kage o Ubae! Mugiwara Ichimi Tai CP9" (Japanese:5つの鍵を奪え! 麦わら一味対CP9) Takahiro Imamura Koga Naoki November 12, 2006(2006-11-12)[32] January 25, 2015

After emerging from the rubble caused by Rocket Man crashing into the Tower of Law, the Straw Hats and Franky are greeted by the blabbermouth CP9 agent Fukurou as he reveals that Spandam has given CP9 orders to execute the intruders. Also explaining that Spandam and Lucci are taking Robin to the Gates of Justice, Fukurou adds that he and four other CP9 members each possess a key that may unlock thesea stonehandcuffs on Robin. As Luffy chases after Robin, the Straw Hats and Franky pursue the keys and each encounter a CP9 member. At the same time, Chimney and her pet rabbit Gonbe accidentally find a secret passage and end up following Spandam and Lucci as they take Robin to the Gates of Justice.
